test_zero_range:
assert [1, 2, 3, 4, 5] == []
  Left contains 5 more items, first extra item: 1
  Full diff:
  - []
  + [1, 2, 3, 4, 5]
test_even_range:
assert [1, 2, 3, 4, 5] == [2, 4, 6, 8, 10, 12]
  At index 0 diff: 1 != 2
  Right contains one more item: 12
  Full diff:
  - [2, 4, 6, 8, 10, 12]
  + [1, 2, 3, 4, 5]
